Sollers has often explained his pseudonym as meaning "tout entier art," not only total devo-
tion to art, but more importantly, completely artful, precisely in the sense of the wily fox. My
Latin dictionary defines "sollers" as possessed entirely of an art, hence clever, skillful, adroit.</mixed-citation>
         </ref>
